        The constructor for the Faculty object type. Uses the super method to retrieve every parameter but maxCourses. Uses the setMaxCourses method to set the maxCourses to the parameter value.
        Parameters:
        firstName - the first name of the faculty member
        lastName - the last name of the faculty member
        id - the user id of the faculty member
        email - the email of the faculty member
        password - the password of the faculty member
        maxCourses - the max courses the faculty member teaches
